      "content": "Grok CAD knowledge base Grok CAD RD CAD web app Conversation with Grok: Web based CAD Tool Drawer left & right sidebars Permanent or Persistent Drawer on the left Feature tree Browser Layers Use MUI X TreeView with TreeItem for the parametric feature history very common in CAD . Right drawer: Properties panel → Dimensions Constraints Material Appearance"
