      "content": "NeuraLink BCI Overcoming serial attention limitation 1. Whole Brain High Bandwidth “Symbiosis Layer” Gigabit Scale Conceptual Telepathy Multiple cortical threads or future multi implant arrays simultaneously ingest raw data streams from any source — live YouTube channels, X feeds, books, papers, podcasts."
