      "url": "/en/math-mdx-page/index",
      "content": "Comprehensive Math Formula Showcase & Test Library This document provides a triple rendering configuration test sheet to verify naked formulas in default mode, naked formulas in moonlight color mode, and custom card components. 1. Core Integration Demonstration Basic Definite Integral Default Style: $$ \\int ^ x^2 \\,dx = \\frac $$ Moonlight II Style: $$ \\int ^ x^2 \\,dx = \\frac $$ MathBlock Card Style: $$ \\int ^ x^2 \\,dx = \\frac $$ Shiki Code Block Alternative math \\int ^ x^2 \\,dx = \\frac 2. Physics & Quantum Mechanics Examples Standard Einstein Mass Energy Equivalence Default Style: $$ E = mc^2 $$ Moonlight II Style: $$ E = mc^2 $$ MathBlock Card Style: $$ E = mc^2 $$ Time Dependent Schrödinger Formulation Default Style: $$ i\\hbar \\frac \\Psi \\mathbf ,t = \\hat \\Psi \\mathbf ,t $$ Moonlight II Style: $$ i\\hbar \\frac \\Psi \\mathbf ,t = \\hat \\Psi \\mathbf ,t $$ MathBlock Card Style: $$ i\\hbar \\frac \\Psi \\mathbf ,t = \\hat \\Psi \\mathbf ,t $$ 3. Advanced Custom Macro Styling & Color Maps Inline Token Highlighting Default Style: $$ f x = \\textcolor \\textcolor ^2 + \\textcolor \\textcolor + \\textcolor $$ Moonlight II Style: $$ f x = \\textcolor \\textcolor ^2 + \\textcolor \\textcolor + \\textcolor $$ MathBlock Card Style: $$ f x = \\textcolor \\textcolor ^2 + \\textcolor \\textcolor + \\textcolor $$ Complex Vector Boundaries Default Style: $$ \\textcolor = \\frac $$ Moonlight II Style: $$ \\textcolor = \\frac $$ MathBlock Card Style: $$ \\textcolor = \\frac $$ Palette Variable Layout Definition Default Style: $$ \\definecolor \\definecolor \\definecolor \\int ^ \\textcolor \\,dx = \\frac \\textcolor $$ Moonlight II Style: $$ \\definecolor \\definecolor \\definecolor \\int ^ \\textcolor \\,dx = \\frac \\textcolor $$ MathBlock Card Style: $$ \\definecolor \\definecolor \\definecolor \\int ^ \\textcolor \\,dx = \\frac \\textcolor $$ Chemical Formula Processing Default Style: $$ \\ce $$ Moonlight II Style: $$ \\ce $$ MathBlock Card Style: $$ \\ce $$ 4. Standard Mathematical Structures Quadratic Equation Formula Default Style: $$ x = \\frac $$ Moonlight II Style: $$ x = \\frac $$ MathBlock Card Style: $$ x = \\frac $$ Infinite Basel Problem Series Default Style: $$ \\sum ^ \\frac = \\frac $$ Moonlight II Style: $$ \\sum ^ \\frac = \\frac $$ MathBlock Card Style: $$ \\sum ^ \\frac = \\frac $$ Multi Variable Double Integrals Default Style: $$ \\iint R f x, y \\,dx \\,dy $$ Moonlight II Style: $$ \\iint R f x, y \\,dx \\,dy $$ MathBlock Card Style: $$ \\iint R f x, y \\,dx \\,dy $$ 5. High Complexity Core System Matrices Linear Systems & Vectors Transformation Matrix Default Style: $$ \\begin a & a & \\cdots & a \\\\ a & a & \\cdots & a \\\\ \\vdots & \\vdots & \\ddots & \\vdots \\\\ a & a & \\cdots & a \\end \\begin x 1 \\\\ x 2 \\\\ \\vdots \\\\ x n \\end = \\begin b 1 \\\\ b 2 \\\\ \\vdots \\\\ b m \\end $$ Moonlight II Style: $$ \\begin a & a & \\cdots & a \\\\ a & a & \\cdots & a \\\\ \\vdots & \\vdots & \\ddots & \\vdots \\\\ a & a & \\cdots & a \\end \\begin x 1 \\\\ x 2 \\\\ \\vdots \\\\ x n \\end = \\begin b 1 \\\\ b 2 \\\\ \\vdots \\\\ b m \\end $$ MathBlock Card Style: $$ \\begin a & a & \\cdots & a \\\\ a & a & \\cdots & a \\\\ \\vdots & \\vdots & \\ddots & \\vdots \\\\ a & a & \\cdots & a \\end \\begin x 1 \\\\ x 2 \\\\ \\vdots \\\\ x n \\end = \\begin b 1 \\\\ b 2 \\\\ \\vdots \\\\ b m \\end $$ 3x3 Matrix Determinants Evaluation Default Style: $$ \\det A = \\begin a & b & c \\\\ d & e & f \\\\ g & h & i \\end = a ei fh b di fg + c dh eg $$ Moonlight II Style: $$ \\det A = \\begin a & b & c \\\\ d & e & f \\\\ g & h & i \\end = a ei fh b di fg + c dh eg $$ MathBlock Card Style: $$ \\det A = \\begin a & b & c \\\\ d & e & f \\\\ g & h & i \\end = a ei fh b di fg + c dh eg $$ Multi Conditional Piecewise Functions Default Style: $$ f x = \\begin x^2 & \\text x 0 \\end $$ Moonlight II Style: $$ f x = \\begin x^2 & \\text x 0 \\end $$ MathBlock Card Style: $$ f x = \\begin x^2 & \\text x 0 \\end $$ Multi step Derivation Proof Alignments Default Style: $$ \\begin x + 3 x 4 &= x x 4 + 3 x 4 \\\\ &= x^2 4x + 3x 12 \\\\ &= x^2 x 12 \\end $$ Moonlight II Style: $$ \\begin x + 3 x 4 &= x x 4 + 3 x 4 \\\\ &= x^2 4x + 3x 12 \\\\ &= x^2 x 12 \\end $$ MathBlock Card Style: $$ \\begin x + 3 x 4 &= x x 4 + 3 x 4 \\\\ &= x^2 4x + 3x 12 \\\\ &= x^2 x 12 \\end $$ 6. Advanced Physics & Field Equations Full Wave Quantum Hamiltonians Default Style: $$ i\\hbar \\frac \\Psi \\mathbf ,t = \\left \\frac \\nabla^2 + V \\mathbf ,t \\right \\Psi \\mathbf ,t $$ Moonlight II Style: $$ i\\hbar \\frac \\Psi \\mathbf ,t = \\left \\frac \\nabla^2 + V \\mathbf ,t \\right \\Psi \\mathbf ,t $$ MathBlock Card Style: $$ i\\hbar \\frac \\Psi \\mathbf ,t = \\left \\frac \\nabla^2 + V \\mathbf ,t \\right \\Psi \\mathbf ,t $$ Boltzmann Statistical Configuration Entropy Default Style: $$ S = k B \\ln \\Omega $$ Moonlight II Style: $$ S = k B \\ln \\Omega $$ MathBlock Card Style: $$ S = k B \\ln \\Omega $$ Classical Limit Derivative Foundations Default Style: $$ f' x = \\lim \\frac $$ Moonlight II Style: $$ f' x = \\lim \\frac $$ MathBlock Card Style: $$ f' x = \\lim \\frac $$ Classical Electrodynamics: Maxwell's Partial Differential Fields Default Style: $$ \\begin \\nabla \\cdot \\mathbf &= \\frac \\\\ \\nabla \\cdot \\mathbf &= 0 \\\\ \\nabla \\times \\mathbf &= \\frac \\\\ \\nabla \\times \\mathbf &= \\mu 0 \\left \\mathbf + \\varepsilon 0 \\frac \\right \\end $$ Moonlight II Style: $$ \\begin \\nabla \\cdot \\mathbf &= \\frac \\\\ \\nabla \\cdot \\mathbf &= 0 \\\\ \\nabla \\times \\mathbf &= \\frac \\\\ \\nabla \\times \\mathbf &= \\mu 0 \\left \\mathbf + \\varepsilon 0 \\frac \\right \\end $$ MathBlock Card Style: $$ \\begin \\nabla \\cdot \\mathbf &= \\frac \\\\ \\nabla \\cdot \\mathbf &= 0 \\\\ \\nabla \\times \\mathbf &= \\frac \\\\ \\nabla \\times \\mathbf &= \\mu 0 \\left \\mathbf + \\varepsilon 0 \\frac \\right \\end $$"
