      "url": "/de/adrs/compressing-mars-terraforming-adr/decisions/ai-supremacy",
      "content": "Compressing Mars Terraforming from 100,000+ to 10 years Assumptions and Breakthroughs Required This 10 year feat assumes: MNT Mastery: Nanobots replicate without errors, scaling from grams to exatons in weeks. Energy Abundance: Portable fusion or beamed solar power unlimited operations. AI Supremacy: Quantum AGI predicts climate dynamics with 100% accuracy, avoiding tipping points. Logistics: Fleets of 1,000+ Starships deliver initial seeds; in space manufacturing handles the rest."
