      "url": "/de/adrs/compressing-mars-terraforming-adr/decisions/biosphere-introduction",
      "content": "Compressing Mars Terraforming from 100,000+ to 10 years Phase 3: Ecosystem Stabilization and Human Habitation Years 6 10 Biosphere Introduction Years 6 8 : Release engineered ecosystems: Nano seeded algae and lichens form soil, while bio nano insects pollinate. AI directed nanobots terraform terrain—eroding canyons into fertile plains and creating rivers. Fusion powered orbital lasers vaporize comets for water imports if needed, accelerating hydrological cycles."
